file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Qinglong API
  description: 在 `系统设置 -> 应用设置 -> 添加应用` 生成 `client_id` 和 `client_secret`
  version: '2022-02-12'
  contact:
    name: Qinglong API
    url: https://github.com/whyour/qinglong/tree/develop/back/api
servers:
  - description: OpenAPI
    url: http://192.168.50.125:5700/open
  - description: SystemAPI
    url: http://192.168.50.125:5700/api
tags:
  - name: 用户
    description: User
  - name: 环境变量
    description: Env
  - name: 配置管理
    description: Config
  - name: 任务日志
    description: Log
  - name: 定时任务
    description: Cron
  - name: 脚本管理
    description: Script
  - name: 依赖管理
    description: Dependence `貌似有点问题？待排查`
  - name: 系统管理
    description: System
  - name: OpenAPI
    description: Open
  
paths:
  /auth/token:
    get:
      tags:
        - 用户
      summary: 获取用户密钥
      parameters:
        - name: client_id
          in: query
          description: Client ID
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: client_secret
          in: query
          description: Client Secret
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        '200':
          description: 返回用户密钥信息
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                properties:
                  code:
                    type: integer
                    example: 200
                  data:
                    properties:
                      token:
                        type: string
                        description: 授权密钥
                      token_type:
                        type: string
                        description: 标记类型
                      expiration:
                        type: integer
                        description: 有效期 默认30天
  /user/login:
    post:
      tags:
        - 用户
      summary: 系统接口登录获取用户密钥
      requestBody:
        description: 登录
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              properties:
                username:
                  type: string
                  description: 用户名
                password:
                  type: string
                  description: 密码
      responses:
        '200':
          description: 返回用户密钥信息
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                properties:
                  code:
                    type: integer
                    example: 200
                  data:
                    properties:
                      token:
                        type: string
                        description: 授权密钥
                      lastip:
                        type: string
                        description: 登录IP
                      lastaddr:
                        type: string
                        description: 登录IP归属地
                      lastlogon:
                        type: integer
                      retries:
                        type: integer
                      platform:
                        type: string
                        description: 登录设备
  /envs:
    get:
      tags:
        - 环境变量
      summary: 获取所有环境变量详情
      description: 使用 Token 返回环境变量详情
      security:
        - HTTPBearer: []
      responses:
        '200':
          description: 返回所有环境变量
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                properties:
                  code:
                    type: integer
                    example: 200
                  data:
                    type: array
                    items:
                      type: object
                      properties:
                        id:
                          type: integer
                          description: 变量 ID
                        value:
                          type: string
                          description: 变量值
                          example: 变量值
                        timestamp:
                          type: string
                          description: 时间戳
                          example: Thu Jan 27 2022 11:22:51 GMT+0800 (中国标准时间)
                        status:
                          type: integer
                        position:
                          type: integer
                        name:
                          type: string
                          description: 变量名
                          example: 变量名
                        remarks:
                          type: string
                          description: 备注
                          example: 备注
                        createdAt:
                          type: string
                          example: "2022-02-01T03:00:53.572Z"
                        updatedAt:
                          type: string
                          example: "2022-02-10T03:30:08.079Z"
        '401':
          description: 未授权
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                properties:
                  code:
                    type: integer
                    example: 401
                  message:
                    type: string
                    example: UnauthorizedError
    post:
      tags:
        - 环境变量
      summary: 添加环境变量
      description: 使用 Token 添加环境变量
      security:
        - HTTPBearer: []
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              properties:
                value:
                  type: string
                  description: 变量值
                  example: 变量值
                name:
                  type: string
                  description: 变量名
                  example: 变量名
                remarks:
                  type: string
                  description: 备注
                  example: 备注
      responses:
        '200':
          description: 成功
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                properties:
                  code:
                    type: integer
                    example: 200
        '401':
          description: 未授权
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                properties:
                  code:
                    type: integer
                    example: 401
                  message:
                    type: string
                    example: UnauthorizedError
    put:
      tags:
        - 环境变量
      summary: 更新环境变量
      description: 使用 Token 更新环境变量
      security:
        - HTTPBearer: []
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              properties:
                value:
                  type: string
                  description: 变量值
                  example: 变量值
                name:
                  type: string
                  description: 变量名
                  example: 变量名
                remarks:
                  type: string
                  description: 备注
                  example: 备注
                id:
                  type: integer
                  description: 变量 ID
      responses:
        '200':
          description: 成功
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                properties:
                  code:
                    type: integer
                    example: 200
        '401':
          description: 未授权
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                properties:
                  code:
                    type: integer
                    example: 401
                  message:
                    type: string
                    example: UnauthorizedError
    delete:
      tags:
        - 环境变量
      summary: 删除环境变量
      description: 使用 Token 删除环境变量
      security:
        - HTTPBearer: []
      requestBody:
        description: 变量 ID 可多个ID
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: array
              description: 变量 ID
              items:
                type: integer
      responses:
        '200':
          description: 成功
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                properties:
                  code:
                    type: integer
                    example: 200
        '401':
          description: 未授权
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                properties:
                  code:
                    type: integer
                    example: 401
                  message:
                    type: string
                    example: UnauthorizedError
  /envs/{id}:
    get:
      tags:
        - 环境变量
      summary: 根据 ID 获取环境变量
      description: 使用 Token 获取环境变量详情
      security:
        - HTTPBearer: []
      parameters:
        - name: id
          in: path
          description: 变量 ID
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
      responses:
        '200':
          description: 返回该变量 ID 的环境变量详情
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                properties:
                  code:
                    type: integer
                    example: 200
                  data:
                    properties:
                      id:
                        type: integer
                        description: 变量 ID
                      value:
                        type: string
                        description: 变量值
                        example: 变量值
                      timestamp:
                        type: string
                        description: 时间戳
                        example: Thu Jan 27 2022 11:22:51 GMT+0800 (中国标准时间)
                      status:
                        type: integer
                      position:
                        type: integer
                      name:
                        type: string
                        description: 变量名
                        example: 变量名
                      remarks:
                        type: string
                        description: 备注
                        example: 备注
                      createdAt:
                        type: string
                        example: "2022-02-01T03:00:53.572Z"
                      updatedAt:
                        type: string
                        example: "2022-02-10T03:30:08.079Z"
        '401':
          description: 未授权
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                properties:
                  code:
                    type: integer
                    example: 401
                  message:
                    type: string
                    example: UnauthorizedError
  /envs/{id}/move:
    get:
      tags:
        - 环境变量
      summary: move
      description: 使用 Token move
      security:
        - HTTPBearer: []
      parameters:
        - name: id
          in: path
          description: 变量 ID
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
      requestBody:
        description: 变量 ID 可多个ID
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              properties:
                fromIndex:
                  type: integer
                toIndex:
                  type: integer
      responses:
        '200':
          description: 返回该变量 ID 的环境变量详情
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                properties:
                  code:
                    type: integer
                    example: 200
                  data:
                    properties:
                      id:
                        type: integer
                        description: 变量 ID
                      value:
                        type: string
                        description: 变量值
                        example: 变量值
                      timestamp:
                        type: string
                        description: 时间戳
                        example: Thu Jan 27 2022 11:22:51 GMT+0800 (中国标准时间)
                      status:
                        type: integer
                      position:
                        type: integer
                      name:
                        type: string
                        description: 变量名
                        example: 变量名
                      remarks:
                        type: string
                        description: 备注
                        example: 备注
                      createdAt:
                        type: string
                        example: "2022-02-01T03:00:53.572Z"
                      updatedAt:
                        type: string
                        example: "2022-02-10T03:30:08.079Z"
        '401':
          description: 未授权
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                properties:
                  code:
                    type: integer
                    example: 401
                  message:
                    type: string
                    example: UnauthorizedError                
  /envs/disable:
    put:
      tags:
        - 环境变量
      summary: 禁用环境变量
      description: 使用 Token 禁用环境变量
      security:
        - HTTPBearer: []
      requestBody:
        description: 变量 ID 可多个ID
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: array
              description: 变量 ID
              items:
                type: integer
      responses:
        '200':
          description: 成功
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                properties:
                  code:
                    type: integer
                    example: 200
        '401':
          description: 未授权
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                properties:
                  code:
                    type: integer
                    example: 401
                  message:
                    type: string
                    example: UnauthorizedError
  /envs/enable:
    put:
      tags:
        - 环境变量
      summary: 启用环境变量
      description: 使用 Token 启用环境变量
      security:
        - HTTPBearer: []
      requestBody:
        description: 变量 ID 可多个ID
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: array
              description: 变量 ID
              items:
                type: integer
      responses:
        '200':
          description: 成功
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                properties:
                  code:
                    type: integer
                    example: 200
        '401':
          description: 未授权
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                properties:
                  code:
                    type: integer
                    example: 401
                  message:
                    type: string
                    example: UnauthorizedError
  /envs/name:
    put:
      tags:
        - 环境变量
      summary: 修改环境变量名
      description: 使用 Token 修改环境变量名
      security:
        - HTTPBearer: []
      requestBody:
        description: 变量 ID 可多个ID
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              properties:
                ids:
                  type: integer
                  description: 变量 ID
                name:
                  type: string
                  description: 变量名
                  example: 变量名
      responses:
        '200':
          description: 成功
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                properties:
                  code:
                    type: integer
                    example: 200
        '401':
          description: 未授权
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                properties:
                  code:
                    type: integer
                    example: 401
                  message:
                    type: string
                    example: UnauthorizedError
  /configs/files:  
    get:
        tags:
          - 配置管理
        summary: 获取配置文件列表
        description: 使用 Token 获取配置文件列表
        security:
          - HTTPBearer: []
        responses:
          '200':
            description: 成功
            content:
              application/json:
                schema:
                  properties:
                    code:
                      type: integer
                      example: 200
                    data:
                      type: array
                      items:
                        type: object
                        properties:
                          title:
                            type: string
                            description: 配置文件名
                          value:
                            type: string
                            description: 配置文件值
          '401':
            description: 未授权
            content:
              application/json:
                schema:
                  properties:
                    code:
                      type: integer
                      example: 401
                    message:
                      type: string
                      example: UnauthorizedError
  /configs/{file}:
    get:
        tags:
          - 配置管理
        summary: 获取配置文件内容
        description: 使用 Token 获取配置文件内容
        security:
          - HTTPBearer: []
        parameters:
          - name: file
            in: path
            description: 配置文件名
            required: true
            schema:
              type: string
        responses:
          '200':
            description: 成功
            content:
              application/json:
                schema:
                  properties:
                    code:
                      type: integer
                      example: 200
                    data:
                      type: string
                      description: 配置文件内容
                      example: 配置文件内容
          '401':
            description: 未授权
            content:
              application/json:
                schema:
                  properties:
                    code:
                      type: integer
                      example: 401
                    message:
                      type: string
                      example: UnauthorizedError
  /configs/save:
    post:
        tags:
          - 配置管理
        summary: 保存配置文件
        description: 使用 Token 获取配置文件列表
        security:
          - HTTPBearer: []
        requestBody:
          description: 保存配置文件
          required: true
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                properties:
                  name:
                    type: string
                    description: 配置文件名
                  content:
                    type: string
                    description: 内容
        responses:
          '200':
            description: 成功
            content:
              application/json:
                schema:
                  properties:
                    code:
                      type: integer
                      example: 200
                    message:
                      type: string
                      example: 保存成功
          '401':
            description: 未授权
            content:
              application/json:
                schema:
                  properties:
                    code:
                      type: integer
                      example: 401
                    message:
                      type: string
                      example: UnauthorizedError
          '403':
            description: 失败
            content:
              application/json:
                schema:
                  properties:
                    code:
                      type: integer
                      example: 401
                    message:
                      type: string
                      example: 文件无法访问
  /logs:
    get:
        tags:
          - 任务日志
        summary: 获取所有任务日志列表
        description: 使用 Token 获取所有任务日志列表
        security:
          - HTTPBearer: []
        responses:
          '200':
            description: 成功
            content:
              application/json:
                schema:
                  properties:
                    code:
                      type: integer
                      example: 200
                    isDir:
                      type: boolean
                    files:
                      type: array
                      items:
                        type: string
                        properties:
                          items:
                            type: string
          '401':
            description: 未授权
            content:
              application/json:
                schema:
                  properties:
                    code:
                      type: integer
                      example: 401
                    message:
                      type: string
                      example: UnauthorizedError
  /logs/{dir}/{file}:
    get:
        tags:
          - 任务日志
        summary: 获取任务日志
        description: 使用 Token 获取任务日志
        security:
          - HTTPBearer: []
        parameters:
          - name: dir
            in: path
            description: 日志目录
            required: true
            schema:
              type: string
          - name: file
            in: path
            description: 日志文件名
            required: true
            schema:
              type: string
        responses:
          '200':
            description: 成功
            content:
              application/json:
                schema:
                  properties:
                    code:
                      type: integer
                      example: 200
                    data:
                      type: string
                      example: 日志文件内容
          '401':
            description: 未授权
            content:
              application/json:
                schema:
                  properties:
                    code:
                      type: integer
                      example: 401
                    message:
                      type: string
                      example: UnauthorizedError
  /logs/{file}:
    get:
        tags:
          - 任务日志
        summary: 获取任务日志
        description: 使用 Token 获取任务日志
        security:
          - HTTPBearer: []
        parameters:
          - name: file
            in: path
            description: 日志文件名
            required: true
            schema:
              type: string
        responses:
          '200':
            description: 成功
            content:
              application/json:
                schema:
                  properties:
                    code:
                      type: integer
                      example: 200
                    data:
                      type: string
                      example: 日志文件内容
          '401':
            description: 未授权
            content:
              application/json:
                schema:
                  properties:
                    code:
                      type: integer
                      example: 401
                    message:
                      type: string
                      example: UnauthorizedError
  /crons:
    get:
      tags:
        - 定时任务
      summary: 获取所有任务详情
      description: 使用 Token 返回定时任务详情
      security:
        - HTTPBearer: []
      responses:
        '200':
          description: 返回定时任务详情
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                properties:
                  code:
                    type: integer
                    example: 200
                  data:
                    type: array
                    items:
                      type: object
                      properties:
                        id:
                          type: integer
                          description: 任务 ID
                        name:
                          type: string
                          description: 任务名称
                          example: 任务名
                        command:
                          type: string
                          description: 任务命令
                          example: task helloworld.py
                        schedule:
                          type: string
                          description: 任务定时
                          example: 0 0 * * *
                        timestamp:
                          type: string
                          description: 时间戳
                          example: Wed Feb 09 2022 13:08:45 GMT+0800 (中国标准时间)
                        saved:
                          type: boolean
                        status:
                          type: integer
                          example: 1
                        isSystem:
                          type: integer
                        pid:
                          type: integer
                          example: null
                        isDisabled:
                          type: integer
                        isPinned:
                          type: integer
                        log_path:
                          type: string
                        labels:
                          type: array
                          description: 任务标签
                          items:
                            type: string
                            example: 标签
                        last_running_time:
                          type: integer
                        last_execution_time:
                          type: integer
                        createdAt:
                          type: string
                          example: "2022-02-09T05:08:45.450Z"
                        updatedAt:
                          type: string
                          example: "2022-02-09T05:50:03.062Z"
        '401':
          description: 未授权
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                properties:
                  code:
                    type: integer
                    example: 401
                  message:
                    type: string
                    example: UnauthorizedError
    post:
      tags:
        - 定时任务
      summary: 添加任务
      description: 使用 Token 添加任务
      security:
        - HTTPBearer: []
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              properties:
                command:
                  type: string
                  description: 任务命令
                  example: task helloworld.py
                schedule:
                  type: string
                  description: 任务定时
                  example: 0 0 * * *
                name:
                  type: string
                  description: 任务名
                  example: 任务名
                labels:
                  type: string
                  description: 标签
                  example: 标签
      responses:
        '200':
          description: 成功
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                properties:
                  code:
                    type: integer
                    example: 200
        '401':
          description: 未授权
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                properties:
                  code:
                    type: integer
                    example: 401
                  message:
                    type: string
                    example: UnauthorizedError
    put:
      tags:
        - 定时任务
      summary: 更新任务
      description: 使用 Token 更新任务
      security:
        - HTTPBearer: []
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              properties:
                labels:
                  type: string
                  description: 标签
                  example: 标签
                command:
                  type: string
                  description: 任务命令
                  example: task helloworld.py
                schedule:
                  type: string
                  description: 任务定时
                  example: 0 0 * * *
                name:
                  type: string
                  description: 任务名
                  example: 任务名
                id:
                  type: integer
                  description: 任务 ID
      responses:
        '200':
          description: 成功
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                properties:
                  code:
                    type: integer
                    example: 200
        '401':
          description: 未授权
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                properties:
                  code:
                    type: integer
                    example: 401
                  message:
                    type: string
                    example: UnauthorizedError
    delete:
      tags:
        - 定时任务
      summary: 删除任务
      description: 使用 Token 删除任务
      security:
        - HTTPBearer: []
      requestBody:
        description: 任务 ID 可多个ID
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: array
              description: 任务 ID
              items:
                type: integer
      responses:
        '200':
          description: 成功
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                properties:
                  code:
                    type: integer
                    example: 200
        '401':
          description: 未授权
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                properties:
                  code:
                    type: integer
                    example: 401
                  message:
                    type: string
                    example: UnauthorizedError
  /crons/{id}:
    get:
      tags:
        - 定时任务
      summary: 根据 ID 获取任务日志
      description: 使用 Token 获取定时任务详情
      security:
        - HTTPBearer: []
      parameters:
        - name: id
          in: path
          description: 任务 ID
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
      responses:
        '200':
          description: 返回该变量 ID 的定时任务详情
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                properties:
                  code:
                    type: integer
                    example: 200
                  data:
                    properties:
                      id:
                        type: integer
                        description: 任务 ID
                      name:
                        type: string
